<h2>Aside 1.5.6</h2>

<p class="intro">A small polish release for tooltips.</p>

<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
  <li><b>Tooltips are no longer cut off.</b> Hovering a control at the notch (like the &times; on a meeting suggestion) showed a tooltip that was clipped by the notch's edge. Tooltips now render above the panel frame everywhere &mdash; at the notch, on the floating pill, in the panel, and in the Aside window.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Changed</h3>
<ul>
  <li><b>Fewer tooltips.</b> Buttons with a visible label (Join, Record, Stop) no longer repeat themselves in a tooltip. Tooltips stay where they add something: icon-only buttons and actions with non-obvious consequences.</li>
</ul>
